<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_transactional_memory" title="Software transactional memory">Software transactional memory</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transactional_Synchronization_Extensions" title="Transactional Synchronization Extensions">Transactional Synchronization Extensions</a></li>
</ul>
